Package it.polimi.ingsw.am01.model.card.face.corner

Class Corner

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.am01.model.card.face.corner.Corner
public class Corner extends Object
A corner in a BaseCardFace. It may be either missing or not. If it's not missing, it can either contain a Collectible or be empty.
